#. module: l10n_hk
#: model_terms:res.company,invoice_terms_html:l10n_hk.demo_company_hk
msgid ""
"HK Company undertakes to do its best to supply performant services in due "
"time in accordance with the agreed timeframes. However, none of its "
"obligations can be considered as being an obligation to achieve results. HK "
"Company cannot under any circumstances, be required by the client to appear "
"as a third party in the context of any claim for damages filed against the "
"client by an end consumer."
msgstr ""
"香港公司承諾竭盡所能，依照約定時限，如期提供高效服務。然而，該公司的任何責任"
"，均不可視為達成特定結果之責任及承諾。在任何情況下，如有最終消費者針對任何損"
"害，向客戶提出申索/索賠，客戶均不得要求香港公司作為第三方加入相關申索/索賠。"

#. module: l10n_hk
#: model_terms:res.company,invoice_terms_html:l10n_hk.demo_company_hk
msgid ""
"If a payment is still outstanding more than sixty (60) days after the due "
"payment date, HK Company reserves the right to call on the services of a "
"debt recovery company. All legal expenses will be payable by the client."
msgstr ""
"若款項逾期超過六十 (60) 天仍未清繳，香港公司保留委託催收/追債公司處理的權利。"
"所有法律費用將由客戶承擔。"

#. module: l10n_hk
#: model_terms:res.company,invoice_terms_html:l10n_hk.demo_company_hk
msgid ""
"In order for it to be admissible, HK Company must be notified of any claim "
"by means of a letter sent by recorded delivery to its registered office "
"within 8 days of the delivery of the goods or the provision of the services."
msgstr ""
"索賠/申索必須在貨物完成交付或服務提供後 8 天內，透過掛號信件/掛號郵遞，寄送至"
"香港公司的註冊辦事處通知該公司，否則索賠/申索將不獲接納。"

