#. module: l10n_hk
#: model_terms:res.company,invoice_terms_html:l10n_hk.demo_company_hk
msgid ""
"Our invoices are payable within 21 working days, unless another payment "
"timeframe is indicated on either the invoice or the order. In the event of "
"non-payment by the due date, HK Company reserves the right to request a "
"fixed interest payment amounting to 10% of the sum remaining due. HK Company "
"will be authorized to suspend any provision of services without prior "
"warning in the event of late payment."
msgstr ""
"發票款項須在 21 個工作天內支付，除非發票或訂單有註明其他付款期限。若在到期日"
"前仍未付款，香港公司保留要求支付固定利息的權利，金額為到期未付款項的 10%。若"
"有逾期付款，香港公司將獲授權，可在沒有事先警告的情況下，暫停提供任何服務。"

